name: THE SYMPHONY OF PHENEX
description:
Phenex is one of the Fallen Angels who was sealed by King Solomon. He holds the rank of Great Duke of Hell and has 20 Legions (tribes/troops) of Demons under his command.
The important role of the Phenex is to lead its troops to the pit of destruction through a symphony,
he is also able to teach all about science, poetry, and is very obedient to the summoner.
described as a PHOENIX figure who can sing while holding the violin with a sweet and melodious tone.
